    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>召唤你的单位，制定策略，抵御敌人！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在封印被污染的水晶的同时，阻挡源源不断涌来的敌人入侵！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集资源，召唤盟友单位，击败越来越强大的敌人。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/502ca5d4f6b21671318fadfa3e240a9e.poster.avif?t=1763124192\" width=608 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/502ca5d4f6b21671318fadfa3e240a9e.webm?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/502ca5d4f6b21671318fadfa3e240a9e.mp4?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>召唤墙壁封锁入口，或让坚固的单位站在前线抵挡敌人。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/3f4db7de1690474831b9cdc1e68bc687.poster.avif?t=1763124192\" width=608 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/3f4db7de1690474831b9cdc1e68bc687.webm?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/3f4db7de1690474831b9cdc1e68bc687.mp4?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强化道具，让你的单位变得更加强大。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/923b1a7ae636b07dcb1abf5e8439825f.poster.avif?t=1763124192\" width=608 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/923b1a7ae636b07dcb1abf5e8439825f.webm?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/923b1a7ae636b07dcb1abf5e8439825f.mp4?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>学习强力技能，快速歼灭敌人。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/1d021159095ec437835ddcbaa91cd10d.poster.avif?t=1763124192\" width=608 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/1d021159095ec437835ddcbaa91cd10d.webm?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/1d021159095ec437835ddcbaa91cd10d.mp4?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组合属于你的独特阵容，完成任务！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/e21dde0ea69b412a1985a2fbe241daf8.poster.avif?t=1763124192\" width=608 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/e21dde0ea69b412a1985a2fbe241daf8.webm?t=1763124192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077090/extras/e21dde0ea69b412a1985a2fbe241daf8.mp4?t=1763124192\" type=\"